short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export and enrich your leads with Haystax.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Chrome extension, "Export to Haystax," allows users to seamlessly export and enrich their LinkedIn Sales Navigator leads with Haystax. By integrating directly with LinkedIn, the extension enables users to capture lead information from their Sales Navigator lists and send it to Haystax for further processing and enrichment. With a simple click, users can transfer lead data, including list names and IDs, directly to Haystax, enhancing their lead management workflow. The extension also provides visual feedback by highlighting processed leads, ensuring a smooth and efficient user experience.
